<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AGRMI-PS Assessment Tool</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800&family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --primary: #1a3c5e;
    --secondary: #2e7d9f;
    --accent: #e67e22;
    --success: #27ae60;
    --warning: #f39c12;
    --danger: #e74c3c;
    --light: #f4f8fb;
    --dark: #0d1f2d;
    --border: #dce8f0;
    --text: #2c3e50;
    --muted: #7f8c9a;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
    background: var(--light);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ===== HEADER ===== */
  header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--primary) 60%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 40px 20px 50px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(46,125,159,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  header .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    padding: 5px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  header h1 span { color: #f0c040; }
  header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  header .meta {
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */
  .progress-bar-container {
    background: white;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  }
  .progress-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .progress-track {
    background: var(--border);
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
    width: 0%;
  }

  /* ===== STEPS NAV ===== */
  .steps-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .step-btn {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    background: white;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .step-btn.active {
    background: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: white;
  }
  .step-btn.done {
    background: var(--success);
    border-color: var(--success);
    color: white;
  }

  /* ===== CONTAINER ===== */
  .container {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 16px 60px;
  }

  /* ===== PAGES ===== */
  .page { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.35s ease; }
  .page.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  /* ===== CARD ===== */
  .card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .card-title .icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .card-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-right: 46px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== FORM ===== */
  .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .form-group label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .form-group select,
  .form-group input {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    background: white;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    outline: none;
    appearance: none;
  }
  .form-group select:focus,
  .form-group input:focus {
    border-color: var(--secondary);
  }

  /* ===== DIMENSION HEADER ===== */
  .dim-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .dim-header .dim-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .dim-header h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dim-header p { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ===== QUESTION ===== */
  .question-block {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .question-block.answered {
    border-color: #c8e6c9;
    background: #fafffe;
  }
  .question-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .question-num {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 24px;
    margin-left: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===== LIKERT SCALE ===== */
  .likert-scale {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .likert-option {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 52px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .likert-option input[type="radio"] {
    display: none;
  }
  .likert-option label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px 6px 8px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    background: white;
    text-align: center;
    min-height: 64px;
  }
  .likert-option label .num {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .likert-option label .lbl {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.2;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
  }
  .likert-option input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
    border-color: var(--secondary);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4fa, #d4ecf7);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(46,125,159,0.2);
  }
  .likert-option input[type="radio"]:checked + label .num { color: var(--primary); }
  .likert-option input[type="radio"]:checked + label .lbl { color: var(--secondary); }
  .likert-option:nth-child(5) input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
    border-color: var(--success);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f8ee, #d4f0df);
  }
  .likert-option:nth-child(5) input[type="radio"]:checked + label .num { color: var(--success); }
  .likert-option:nth-child(1) input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
    border-color: var(--danger);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdecea, #fad5d0);
  }
  .likert-option:nth-child(1) input[type="radio"]:checked + label .num { color: var(--danger); }
  .likert-scale-labels {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
    padding: 0 2px;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ===== NAVIGATION BUTTONS ===== */
  .nav-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(26,60,94,0.3);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(26,60,94,0.4);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--secondary);
    background: var(--light);
  }
  .btn-success {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success), #2ecc71);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(39,174,96,0.3);
  }
  .btn-success:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.45;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none !important;
  }

  /* ===== WARNING BOX ===== */
  .warning-box {
    background: #fff8e1;
    border: 1px solid #ffe082;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #7d5a00;
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: none;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .warning-box.show { display: block; }

  /* ===== RESULTS PAGE ===== */
  .score-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), var(--primary));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .score-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -30%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .score-circle {
    width: 130px;
    height: 130px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .score-circle .score-val {
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .score-circle .score-max {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .maturity-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 8px 24px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .maturity-emerging { background: rgba(231,76,60,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(231,76,60,0.5); }
  .maturity-developing { background: rgba(243,156,18,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(243,156,18,0.5); }
  .maturity-established { background: rgba(39,174,96,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(39,174,96,0.5); }
  .maturity-advanced { background: rgba(52,152,219,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(52,152,219,0.5); }

  .dim-scores-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .dim-scores-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .dim-score-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .dim-score-card .dim-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .score-bar-track {
    background: var(--border);
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .score-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }
  .dim-score-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .dim-score-meta .val { font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); }

  .rec-card {
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border-right: 5px solid;
  }
  .rec-high { background: #fdecea; border-color: var(--danger); }
  .rec-med { background: #fff8e1; border-color: var(--warning); }
  .rec-low { background: #e8f8ee; border-color: var(--success); }
  .rec-card .priority {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .rec-high .priority { color: var(--danger); }
  .rec-med .priority { color: #b7770d; }
  .rec-low .priority { color: var(--success); }
  .rec-card .rec-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }
  .comparison-table th {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    text-align: right;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .comparison-table td {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .comparison-table tr:hover td { background: var(--light); }
  .comparison-table .highlight td {
    background: #e8f4fa;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ===== INTRO PAGE ===== */
  .intro-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .intro-hero h2 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .intro-hero p { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .feature-item {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .feature-item .f-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 12px;
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  .feature-item h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 6px; font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; }
  .feature-item p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  .info-note {
    background: #e8f4fa;
    border: 1px solid #b3d7ea;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
  }

  @media print {
    .progress-bar-container, .steps-nav, .nav-buttons, header .meta { display: none; }
    .card { box-shadow: none; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="badge">SUPPLEMENTARY MATERIAL | RESEARCH PROTOTYPE</div>
  <h1>AGRMI-PS <span>Assessment Tool</span></h1>
  <p>AI Governance Readiness Maturity Index for Palestinian Organizations<br>
  Developed as a companion tool to the research paper</p>
  <div class="meta">
    <span>Version 1.0 | 2025</span>
    <span>5 Dimensions | 20 Questions</span>
    <span>Likert Scale 1-5</span>
    <span>West Bank, Palestine</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="progress-bar-container">
  <div class="progress-info">
    <span id="stepLabel">الخطوة 1 من 8</span>
    <span id="pctLabel">0%</span>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-track">
    <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="steps-nav">
  <button class="step-btn active" onclick="goToStep(0)">مقدمة</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(1)">بيانات المنظمة</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(2)">البُعد 1</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(3)">البُعد 2</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(4)">البُعد 3</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(5)">البُعد 4</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(6)">البُعد 5</button>
  <button class="step-btn" onclick="goToStep(7)">النتائج</button>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- PAGE 0: INTRO -->
  <div class="page active" id="page-0">
    <div class="intro-hero">
      <h2>مرحباً بك في أداة AGRMI-PS</h2>
      <p>هذا النموذج الأولي مرافق للورقة البحثية حول جاهزية حوكمة الذكاء الاصطناعي في المنظمات الفلسطينية. يساعدك على تقييم مستوى نضج منظمتك عبر خمسة أبعاد رئيسية.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="f-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a3c5e" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 12h6M9 15h4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>20 سؤالاً</h4>
        <p>موزعة على 5 أبعاد اساسية لحوكمة الذكاء الاصطناعي</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="f-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a3c5e" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>5-10 دقائق</h4>
        <p>الوقت المتوقع لاكمال التقييم بالكامل</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="f-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a3c5e" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2l3 7h7l-6 4 2 7-6-4-6 4 2-7-6-4h7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>نتائج فورية</h4>
        <p>تقرير تفصيلي مع مستوى النضج والتوصيات</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-note">
      <strong>ملاحظة للمقيّم:</strong> يُعبّر كل سؤال عن ممارسة من ممارسات حوكمة الذكاء الاصطناعي. قيّم مدى تطبيق كل ممارسة في منظمتك على مقياس من 1 (غائبة تماماً) إلى 5 (مطبّقة بالكامل وموثّقة). الصدق في الإجابة يُحقق نتائج أكثر دقة ويُساعد في رسم خريطة التطوير.
    </div>
    <div class="nav-buttons" style="justify-content:flex-end">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="nextStep()">
